  "body": "### Description\r\n\r\n*Type*: Bug\r\n\r\n\r\n*Summary*: This issue contains several cosmetic improvements:\r\n- `next` button is overlapped on Android when suggestions are enabled for keyboards. Also, it depends on keyboard size, for ex SWIFT keyboard is bigger than default one and it hides the Next button almost completely\r\n- missing `Done` button on android keyboard\r\n- missing `Done` button on iOS keyboard\r\n\r\n#### Expected behavior\r\n\r\n- keyboard does not hide this Next button\r\n- both android and ios keyboards contain this Done button which could be used as Enter\r\n\r\n@errorists @denis-sharypin please suggest something here if possible\r\n\r\n#### Actual behavior\r\n\r\n![image](https://user-images.githubusercontent.com/28752642/48913159-a53cfa80-ee88-11e8-9f1d-d07e756fa8d5.png)\r\n\r\n![image](https://user-images.githubusercontent.com/28752642/48913176-b128bc80-ee88-11e8-8e3a-1c76d100a69e.png)\r\n\r\n![image](https://user-images.githubusercontent.com/28752642/48913199-bf76d880-ee88-11e8-8e51-41b035d7872d.png)\r\n\r\n\r\n### Reproduction\r\n\r\n- Open Status\r\n- Start creating account untill the step with entering name",
